<title>HEALED BY THE BRUISES OF JESUS</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Lalpa, hun thehzak in,
 Na vangsakna guoh chuh;
 Ka ngaklah ui,
 Thil chin tinchengte hi.
 Zing leh nitak ale,
 Sel in hung pung ina,
 Gamgaw apat.

[V2]
 2. Na lungsietna lopi,
 Ka vela thil gimlim;
 A hung dim hin,
 Mel hetloh gama mi.
 Hung khawm ding a hiu hi,
 Na lungsiet gimlim hi,
 Hun he ta'n au.

[V3]
 3. Nangmah mel hawihtak hin,
 Leisiet a thil tincheng;
 A zawh mai hi,
 Na mel ah thil deihum.
 Tincheng chuh a lang khawm,
 Na liemna ka kipah-nau pen ahi.</lyrics>
</song>